1
00:00:01,120 --> 00:00:04,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They say they feel more 
comfortable with full invisibility.</font>

2
00:00:05,800 --> 00:00:11,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Though I wouldn't say I prefer 
being fully invisible myself.</font>

3
00:00:11,490 --> 00:00:13,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}EPISODE 11: THE INVISIBLE PERSON VILLAGE</font>

4
00:00:24,880 --> 00:00:28,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The next stop is Third 
District Shopping Street.</font>

5
00:00:28,450 --> 00:00:30,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Third District Shopping Street.</font>

6
00:00:34,530 --> 00:00:35,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Akira-san?</font>

7
00:00:37,330 --> 00:00:38,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you all right?</font>

8
00:00:39,040 --> 00:00:40,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, I'm fine.</font>

9
00:00:41,100 --> 00:00:43,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry we had to 
make so many transfers.</font>

10
00:00:44,010 --> 00:00:46,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My hometown is really out there.</font>

11
00:00:46,010 --> 00:00:47,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No problem!</font>

12
00:00:47,190 --> 00:00:50,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm excited to visit 
the invisible person village!</font>

13
00:00:50,320 --> 00:00:51,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's in the middle of nowhere.</font>

14
00:00:51,900 --> 00:00:54,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nothing but fields.</font>

15
00:00:54,080 --> 00:00:55,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's very closed off, too.</font>

16
00:00:55,480 --> 00:00:57,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, really?</font>

17
00:00:58,180 --> 00:01:00,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, it's a rather odd village.</font>

18
00:01:00,800 --> 00:01:02,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">An odd village?</font>

19
00:02:34,000 --> 00:02:35,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}THIRD DISTRICT SHOPPING STREET</font>

20
00:02:39,300 --> 00:02:41,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The air is so fresh!</font>

21
00:02:41,640 --> 00:02:44,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, it's a serene, green place.</font>

22
00:02:52,400 --> 00:02:54,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is the shopping street.</font>

23
00:02:57,290 --> 00:02:59,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see. It's very lively!</font>

24
00:02:59,600 --> 00:03:01,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are these all the locals?</font>

25
00:03:04,520 --> 00:03:06,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I sense so many people!</font>

26
00:03:06,270 --> 00:03:08,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I should have expected that.</font>

27
00:03:09,240 --> 00:03:11,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The village is exempted 
from certain laws,</font>

28
00:03:11,340 --> 00:03:14,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so we're allowed to walk around 
with full invisibility.</font>

29
00:03:14,880 --> 00:03:20,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Many of the invisible people who live 
here go around like that all the time.</font>

30
00:03:20,230 --> 00:03:21,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see!</font>

31
00:03:22,860 --> 00:03:27,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is the people being fully invisible
 what makes the town odd?</font>

32
00:03:27,280 --> 00:03:29,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, it disorients a lot of people,</font>

33
00:03:29,670 --> 00:03:32,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but I suppose it's 
an everyday thing for you.</font>

34
00:03:34,300 --> 00:03:36,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, my family's house is up ahead.</font>

35
00:03:38,480 --> 00:03:40,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you all right, Shizuka-san?</font>

36
00:03:40,250 --> 00:03:42,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I just got really nervous!</font>

37
00:03:42,800 --> 00:03:44,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know how you feel,</font>

38
00:03:44,430 --> 00:03:46,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but I know you can handle it.</font>

39
00:03:46,560 --> 00:03:48,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-Yes! I'll do my best!</font>

40
00:03:52,050 --> 00:03:54,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that... Aki?</font>

41
00:03:56,790 --> 00:04:00,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}TONOME</font>

42
00:03:57,710 --> 00:03:58,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm home!</font>

43
00:04:18,070 --> 00:04:19,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shizuka-san.</font>

44
00:04:19,120 --> 00:04:21,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sitting to your left is my father.</font>

45
00:04:21,360 --> 00:04:22,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To your right is my mother.</font>

46
00:04:23,040 --> 00:04:25,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{M}I-It's so quiet.</i></font>

47
00:04:26,340 --> 00:04:30,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{M}Akira-san's always quiet, 
but they're even quieter.</i></font>

48
00:04:30,910 --> 00:04:34,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{M}It's like... a silent pressure...</i></font>

49
00:04:35,040 --> 00:04:35,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is it?</font>

50
00:04:35,740 --> 00:04:39,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um... My name is Shizuka Yako!</font>

51
00:04:39,660 --> 00:04:43,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Akira-san is always helping me... um...</font>

52
00:04:43,680 --> 00:04:46,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-It's so good to meet you!</font>

53
00:04:47,730 --> 00:04:48,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

54
00:04:49,040 --> 00:04:51,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you for helping our Akira.</font>

55
00:04:51,660 --> 00:04:54,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{M}Her voice is so flat and impersonal.</i></font>

56
00:04:54,320 --> 00:04:57,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{M}Maybe she doesn't like me?</i></font>

57
00:04:57,850 --> 00:05:00,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{M}Wh-What do I do, Akira-san?</i></font>

58
00:05:00,320 --> 00:05:04,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're currently dating 
and considering living together.</font>

59
00:05:04,110 --> 00:05:05,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>R-Right to the point?!</i></font>

60
00:05:06,600 --> 00:05:07,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sounds fine to me.</font>

61
00:05:09,090 --> 00:05:10,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, it sounds fine.</font>

62
00:05:11,160 --> 00:05:14,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Also, I've been wondering...</font>

63
00:05:15,700 --> 00:05:18,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why are you wearing those strange masks?</font>

64
00:05:18,770 --> 00:05:20,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Masks?</font>

65
00:05:22,770 --> 00:05:25,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You said you'd be bringing 
another species by.</font>

66
00:05:25,800 --> 00:05:28,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We thought she'd be more 
comfortable if we had faces.</font>

67
00:05:28,720 --> 00:05:31,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shizuka-san is blind. 
They're not doing much good.</font>

68
00:05:31,680 --> 00:05:33,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ah, fair point.</font>

69
00:05:33,880 --> 00:05:35,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, fair point.</font>

70
00:05:35,200 --> 00:05:37,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thought I told you that.</font>

71
00:05:37,630 --> 00:05:39,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I guess she can't tell.</font>

72
00:05:39,260 --> 00:05:41,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, I guess she can't tell.</font>

73
00:05:41,400 --> 00:05:44,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{M}Well, this might be okay!</i></font>

74
00:05:44,780 --> 00:05:47,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is it all right if we 
turn fully invisible, then?</font>

75
00:05:47,760 --> 00:05:49,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, that's fine.</font>

76
00:05:50,470 --> 00:05:53,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They say they feel more 
comfortable with full invisibility.</font>

77
00:05:53,670 --> 00:05:56,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. That's the case 
for all invisible people.</font>

78
00:05:57,960 --> 00:05:59,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really?</font>

79
00:05:59,740 --> 00:06:04,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fully invisible is how we 
should rightly be, after all.</font>

80
00:06:10,540 --> 00:06:13,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I should take her to meet 
Grandmother next, I suppose.</font>

81
00:06:13,470 --> 00:06:16,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's in her room because of her bad leg.</font>

82
00:06:22,380 --> 00:06:28,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Though I wouldn't say I prefer 
being fully invisible myself.</font>

83
00:06:30,650 --> 00:06:35,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because you like people 
to see your favorite outfits, right?</font>

84
00:06:36,920 --> 00:06:40,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Later, can I tell you all 
the details of the suit I'm wearing now?</font>

85
00:06:41,760 --> 00:06:43,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd love to hear it!</font>

86
00:06:45,800 --> 00:06:47,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Grandma, we're coming in.</font>

87
00:06:48,360 --> 00:06:49,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Welcome!</font>

88
00:06:50,670 --> 00:06:52,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Grandma, Shizuka-san is...</font>

89
00:06:52,590 --> 00:06:55,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I told them to let you know, too!</font>

90
00:06:55,800 --> 00:06:56,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh!</font>

91
00:06:59,510 --> 00:07:01,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In the Warring States period,</font>

92
00:07:01,070 --> 00:07:04,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">we were a house of ninja 
who served our lord well!</font>

93
00:07:09,070 --> 00:07:10,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ninja!</font>

94
00:07:10,440 --> 00:07:13,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You were ninja?! That's amazing!</font>

95
00:07:14,180 --> 00:07:16,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We have shuriken 
and such in the warehouse!</font>

96
00:07:17,160 --> 00:07:20,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">C-Can you do ninjutsu?!</font>

97
00:07:20,080 --> 00:07:26,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Our fully invisible forms certainly 
seemed like ninjutsu to outsiders!</font>

98
00:07:27,130 --> 00:07:30,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But we couldn't make our shuriken 
and other tools invisible,</font>

99
00:07:30,520 --> 00:07:33,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so we had to use various other tricks!</font>

100
00:07:33,220 --> 00:07:35,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I see!</font>

101
00:07:35,360 --> 00:07:36,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}{M}She's very excited.</i></font>

102
00:07:35,860 --> 00:07:38,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So cool! So cool!</font>

103
00:07:36,960 --> 00:07:38,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Akira.</font>

104
00:07:45,240 --> 00:07:47,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey. It's been a while, Aki.</font>

105
00:07:47,960 --> 00:07:50,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kiriguro-san! You're back in town?!</font>

106
00:07:50,780 --> 00:07:52,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's my line.</font>

107
00:07:52,620 --> 00:07:55,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, you've come a long way.</font>

108
00:07:57,220 --> 00:07:59,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I guess I was still in school 
the last time we talked...</font>

109
00:08:00,480 --> 00:08:02,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You were such a little kid.</font>

110
00:08:02,360 --> 00:08:04,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You surprised me, 
dressed up in that suit.</font>

111
00:08:05,330 --> 00:08:08,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm impressed you could 
tell it was me, really.</font>

112
00:08:10,730 --> 00:08:11,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{M}Who's that?</i></font>

113
00:08:15,050 --> 00:08:17,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is Masashi Kiriguro.</font>

114
00:08:17,310 --> 00:08:19,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you remember the story I told you?</font>

115
00:08:20,440 --> 00:08:22,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The first invisible person model...</font>

116
00:08:22,960 --> 00:08:24,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, that one!</font>

117
00:08:24,600 --> 00:08:27,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What kind of introduction is that?</font>

118
00:08:28,110 --> 00:08:29,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We were just talking old times.</font>

119
00:08:29,780 --> 00:08:33,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I retired from modeling. 
Now I run this Italian place.</font>

120
00:08:33,410 --> 00:08:35,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You surprised me, though.</font>

121
00:08:35,040 --> 00:08:39,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was opening the place up this morning 
and thought, "Hey, is that Aki?"</font>

122
00:08:39,030 --> 00:08:42,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm impressed you recognized me. 
It's been over ten years.</font>

123
00:08:42,740 --> 00:08:46,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not many people around here 
who don't do full invisibility.</font>

124
00:08:46,240 --> 00:08:48,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I just kinda figured.</font>

125
00:08:49,920 --> 00:08:51,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here, eat up.</font>

126
00:08:53,510 --> 00:08:54,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It smells wonderful!</font>

127
00:08:54,800 --> 00:08:55,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you for the food.</font>

128
00:08:56,360 --> 00:08:58,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you recognize me, Aki?</font>

129
00:08:58,400 --> 00:09:01,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I didn't have all this ink 
the last time we met.</font>

130
00:09:01,300 --> 00:09:03,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I knew you on sight.</font>

131
00:09:03,230 --> 00:09:06,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When you were a child, you drew 
the patterns on with a pen, right?</font>

132
00:09:08,360 --> 00:09:10,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, right.</font>

133
00:09:10,850 --> 00:09:12,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Guess I haven't changed much either.</font>

134
00:09:13,870 --> 00:09:17,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But you were such a help to me then.</font>

135
00:09:18,360 --> 00:09:19,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, I remember!</font>

136
00:09:19,980 --> 00:09:23,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You were crying your eyes out. 
"I dunno who anyone is!"</font>

137
00:09:23,740 --> 00:09:26,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come on, you don't have to 
bring up that part!</font>

138
00:09:29,250 --> 00:09:30,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You were crying?</font>

139
00:09:31,310 --> 00:09:34,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I grew up surrounded by other species.</font>

140
00:09:36,590 --> 00:09:39,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When I was first brought 
to this village when I was young...</font>

141
00:09:39,840 --> 00:09:42,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, you're all alone?</font>

142
00:09:41,040 --> 00:09:43,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}</i>Come over here! I've got some candy!</font>

143
00:09:43,150 --> 00:09:46,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Being surrounded by invisible people 
at all times frightened me...</font>

144
00:09:43,900 --> 00:09:45,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}</i>What a cutie-pie!</font>

145
00:09:45,700 --> 00:09:46,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}</i>Hey, now!</font>

146
00:09:51,830 --> 00:09:55,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And then I met Kiriguro-san, 
who had drawn on his face.</font>

147
00:09:56,040 --> 00:09:58,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You came from the big city, right?</font>

148
00:10:07,720 --> 00:10:11,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thought, is this kid holding 
a one-man Halloween?</font>

149
00:10:11,440 --> 00:10:12,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey. Lay off.</font>

150
00:10:13,960 --> 00:10:15,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thought you were such a strange child.</font>

151
00:10:16,480 --> 00:10:20,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But you really set me at ease.</font>

152
00:10:20,470 --> 00:10:22,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thinking back now,</font>

153
00:10:22,100 --> 00:10:25,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I drew a lot of different 
things on my face.</font>

154
00:10:25,310 --> 00:10:28,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not sure how I made it as a model.</font>

155
00:10:28,520 --> 00:10:33,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">At the time, he modeled fashions 
as the first invisible model.</font>

156
00:10:33,280 --> 00:10:36,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see! He did!</font>

157
00:10:36,210 --> 00:10:40,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Back then, pretty much 
the only jobs for invisible people</font>

158
00:10:40,750 --> 00:10:44,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">were secret agent stuff 
or stuff here at home.</font>

159
00:10:44,090 --> 00:10:50,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was curious about the big city, 
so I packed a bag and went there.</font>

160
00:11:02,180 --> 00:11:03,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

161
00:11:03,360 --> 00:11:05,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's never been 
an invisible person model before...</font>

162
00:11:06,460 --> 00:11:09,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can see some appeal in showing 
off the outfit's lining...</font>

163
00:11:09,480 --> 00:11:10,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Could be pretty cool.</font>

164
00:11:11,750 --> 00:11:14,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But only for a moment.</font>

165
00:11:15,000 --> 00:11:17,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A moment's intrigue, and then it's over.</font>

166
00:11:20,620 --> 00:11:22,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I mean, if invisibility's 
all you're offering,</font>

167
00:11:22,760 --> 00:11:25,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I could get any invisible person.</font>

168
00:11:28,120 --> 00:11:32,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why does it have to be <i>you</i>?</font>

169
00:11:34,500 --> 00:11:37,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{M}Dammit. Another audition down the drain.</i></font>

170
00:11:37,290 --> 00:11:39,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why does it have to be <i>you</i>?</font>

171
00:11:39,250 --> 00:11:41,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{M}Why it has to me...</i></font>

172
00:11:43,530 --> 00:11:45,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What, did I hit you?!</font>

173
00:11:45,350 --> 00:11:46,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That hurt...</font>

174
00:11:46,400 --> 00:11:49,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Roll your sleeves down! It's not safe!</font>

175
00:11:54,430 --> 00:11:56,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">True enough.</font>

176
00:11:56,940 --> 00:11:58,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">See you later!</font>

177
00:11:58,360 --> 00:11:59,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Later!</font>

178
00:12:00,370 --> 00:12:01,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I mean, if invisibility's 
all you're offering,</font>

179
00:12:01,780 --> 00:12:04,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I could get any invisible person.</font>

180
00:12:04,720 --> 00:12:07,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Roll your sleeves down! It's not safe!</font>

181
00:12:07,730 --> 00:12:11,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{M}No wonder the people back home 
didn't want me to go to the city.</i></font>

182
00:12:11,850 --> 00:12:16,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{M}Life here is too damn hard 
for invisible people.</i></font>

183
00:12:33,660 --> 00:12:36,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If invisibility's all you're offering, 
I could get any invisible person.</font>

184
00:12:37,430 --> 00:12:40,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't tell anything if I can't see you!</font>

185
00:12:40,550 --> 00:12:42,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you even thinking?</font>

186
00:12:43,480 --> 00:12:45,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't you run away!</font>

187
00:12:46,160 --> 00:12:48,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You came here because you wanted to!</font>

188
00:12:49,520 --> 00:12:52,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You should've stayed home 
and lived a normal life!</font>

189
00:12:53,190 --> 00:12:55,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's your fault for leaving!</font>

190
00:13:39,960 --> 00:13:41,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I feel sick.</font>

191
00:13:41,440 --> 00:13:44,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Crap. Big audition today...</font>

192
00:13:44,840 --> 00:13:46,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gotta hurry...</font>

193
00:13:49,230 --> 00:13:51,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What the hell did I do?!</font>

194
00:13:52,560 --> 00:13:54,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shit, shit, shit!</font>

195
00:13:54,170 --> 00:13:56,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've got my audition coming up!</font>

196
00:14:01,070 --> 00:14:02,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No freaking way!</font>

197
00:14:03,700 --> 00:14:05,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So...</font>

198
00:14:05,520 --> 00:14:09,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry for coming 
to the audition looking ridiculous.</font>

199
00:14:09,680 --> 00:14:10,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{M}Dammit.</i></font>

200
00:14:11,120 --> 00:14:13,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{M}Just reject me already.</i></font>

201
00:14:13,770 --> 00:14:16,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're really interesting.</font>

202
00:14:17,220 --> 00:14:18,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, yeah...</font>

203
00:14:18,100 --> 00:14:20,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The "moment's intrigue" thing, right?</font>

204
00:14:20,580 --> 00:14:22,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, you're incredibly interesting.</font>

205
00:14:22,950 --> 00:14:24,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're in.</font>

206
00:14:32,020 --> 00:14:34,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You tattooed a skeleton on yourself</font>

207
00:14:34,320 --> 00:14:38,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and added body paint to match 
whatever design you were wearing.</font>

208
00:14:38,310 --> 00:14:41,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">People loved the way it made 
the clothing stand out.</font>

209
00:14:44,870 --> 00:14:46,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{M}I can't imagine it at all!</i></font>

210
00:14:46,860 --> 00:14:50,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It made the clothing stand out, so I got
calls to model all sorts of collections.</font>

211
00:14:50,870 --> 00:14:54,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Invisible people tend to get lumped 
all together because we can't be seen,</font>

212
00:14:54,510 --> 00:14:56,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but thinking back now,</font>

213
00:14:56,000 --> 00:15:00,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the body paint and tattoos were 
my own way of expressing myself.</font>

214
00:15:02,540 --> 00:15:04,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}EXPRESSING MYSELF</font>

215
00:15:04,900 --> 00:15:08,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's the only way I can 
express myself, after all.</font>

216
00:15:10,200 --> 00:15:11,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Expressing myself...</font>

217
00:15:18,340 --> 00:15:20,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{M}They're so similar.</i></font>

218
00:15:22,920 --> 00:15:24,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey,</font>

219
00:15:24,140 --> 00:15:26,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">don't the people of the village struggle</font>

220
00:15:26,200 --> 00:15:28,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">with everyone being 
invisible all the time?</font>

221
00:15:28,640 --> 00:15:33,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Invisible people have an organ that 
lets them sense other invisible people.</font>

222
00:15:33,030 --> 00:15:38,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We can sense where they are, 
and tell who's who.</font>

223
00:15:38,290 --> 00:15:41,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But the organ that makes 
it possible tends to end up</font>

224
00:15:41,880 --> 00:15:44,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">underdeveloped in those 
who are raised in the city, like me.</font>

225
00:15:46,050 --> 00:15:49,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was around elementary 
school age when I learned</font>

226
00:15:49,400 --> 00:15:53,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">to identify people by their 
unique sounds and smells.</font>

227
00:15:53,180 --> 00:15:55,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that you, Ema-chan?</font>

228
00:15:55,380 --> 00:15:57,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How did you know?!</font>

229
00:15:57,440 --> 00:16:01,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It seems like other people can't do that, 
so it always really surprised them.</font>

230
00:16:01,910 --> 00:16:03,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

231
00:16:03,130 --> 00:16:05,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I suppose we all adjust 
to our surroundings.</font>

232
00:16:05,770 --> 00:16:08,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And since I was raised 
among non-invisible people...</font>

233
00:16:08,840 --> 00:16:09,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes,</font>

234
00:16:09,760 --> 00:16:14,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the reason I learned how to do it isn't 
because I worked really hard at it,</font>

235
00:16:14,400 --> 00:16:17,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">or that other people 
don't work hard at it...</font>

236
00:16:17,300 --> 00:16:21,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was just living my life, being blind,</font>

237
00:16:21,520 --> 00:16:24,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and I guess I adjusted to the need.</font>

238
00:16:24,450 --> 00:16:26,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know exactly what you mean.</font>

239
00:16:26,560 --> 00:16:28,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But...</font>

240
00:16:28,510 --> 00:16:32,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because of that, I was able to find you.</font>

241
00:16:32,180 --> 00:16:33,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So I'm glad!</font>

242
00:16:35,840 --> 00:16:38,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, could you take that somewhere else?</font>

243
00:16:39,220 --> 00:16:40,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Later.</font>

244
00:16:40,100 --> 00:16:41,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you for the meal!</font>

245
00:16:41,640 --> 00:16:43,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aki, make sure you 
stop by again sometime.</font>

246
00:16:43,880 --> 00:16:45,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, I will.</font>

247
00:16:52,880 --> 00:16:56,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{M}Invisible people tend to
 be judged by their invisibility.</i></font>

248
00:16:57,270 --> 00:16:59,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{M}We're treasured because we can't be seen.</i></font>

249
00:16:59,330 --> 00:17:00,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{M}Suspected because
we can't be seen.</i></font>

250
00:17:01,290 --> 00:17:02,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{M}Feared.</i></font>

251
00:17:02,840 --> 00:17:04,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{M}And ignored.</i></font>

252
00:17:05,320 --> 00:17:09,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{M}But that didn't matter to Shizuka-san.</i></font>

253
00:17:17,280 --> 00:17:18,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shizuka-san.</font>

254
00:17:18,320 --> 00:17:19,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes?</font>

255
00:17:21,790 --> 00:17:23,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm so glad I met you.</font>

256
00:17:24,640 --> 00:17:26,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-It's not that big a deal...</font>

257
00:17:26,760 --> 00:17:29,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's just how I feel right now.</font>

258
00:17:29,400 --> 00:17:32,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're always so frank!</font>

259
00:17:32,020 --> 00:17:35,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I'm an invisible person...</font>

260
00:17:35,200 --> 00:17:38,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't express my feelings 
if I don't say them.</font>

261
00:17:44,320 --> 00:17:48,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hearing that... makes my heart race...</font>

262
00:17:49,200 --> 00:17:54,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All the little things you say 
and do make my heart race.</font>

263
00:17:54,170 --> 00:17:56,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You liar!</font>

264
00:17:58,530 --> 00:17:59,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not lying.</font>

265
00:18:11,300 --> 00:18:12,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good, just in time.</font>

266
00:18:12,970 --> 00:18:13,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, Sis.</font>

267
00:18:15,310 --> 00:18:16,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fu-kun!</font>

268
00:18:16,960 --> 00:18:20,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why did you want to come all of a sudden?</font>

269
00:18:22,430 --> 00:18:23,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where's Tonome-san?</font>

270
00:18:23,780 --> 00:18:26,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's not walking you home after work?</font>

271
00:18:26,290 --> 00:18:29,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's still working!</font>

272
00:18:29,040 --> 00:18:31,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Detective work doesn't 
have hard and fast hours!</font>

273
00:18:31,680 --> 00:18:32,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh.</font>

274
00:18:33,220 --> 00:18:34,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Anyway, I'm hungry.</font>

275
00:18:34,830 --> 00:18:36,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take me somewhere good to eat.</font>

276
00:18:36,720 --> 00:18:39,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But it's not payday yet...</font>

277
00:18:42,630 --> 00:18:45,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Dad gave me 10,000 yen for dinner.</font>

278
00:18:45,140 --> 00:18:46,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then off we go!</font>

279
00:18:46,430 --> 00:18:50,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've got some places 
registered in my guidance app...</font>

280
00:18:57,630 --> 00:18:59,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's wrong?</font>

281
00:18:59,800 --> 00:19:01,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's an invisible 
person wearing a suit.</font>

282
00:19:02,200 --> 00:19:03,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It could be Tonome-san.</font>

283
00:19:03,970 --> 00:19:05,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Akira-san's nearby?!</font>

284
00:19:05,530 --> 00:19:07,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll check if it's him.</font>

285
00:19:07,820 --> 00:19:10,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Check if it's him?</font>

286
00:19:13,020 --> 00:19:13,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here.</font>

287
00:19:19,480 --> 00:19:21,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tonome-san...</font>

288
00:19:22,380 --> 00:19:24,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you so much!</font>

289
00:19:26,880 --> 00:19:27,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sis.</font>

290
00:19:27,770 --> 00:19:29,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Welcome back!</font>

291
00:19:29,300 --> 00:19:31,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well? Was it him?</font>

292
00:19:31,230 --> 00:19:33,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tonome is a traitor.</font>

293
00:19:34,330 --> 00:19:35,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm gonna bash him good.</font>

294
00:19:35,480 --> 00:19:37,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you talking about?</font>

295
00:19:38,130 --> 00:19:41,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Honestly. Tailing Akira-san...</font>

296
00:19:41,160 --> 00:19:43,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's a detective. He'll notice you!</font>

297
00:19:43,240 --> 00:19:45,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's the one sneaking around.</font>

298
00:19:45,120 --> 00:19:46,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll whack him either way.</font>

299
00:19:47,120 --> 00:19:49,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's probably a marriage scam.</font>

300
00:19:49,080 --> 00:19:52,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Akira-san would never 
do something like that.</font>

301
00:19:53,300 --> 00:19:57,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And you haven't done enough investigation 
to confirm that he's cheating.</font>

302
00:19:57,810 --> 00:20:00,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, I saw him give her the ring.</font>

303
00:20:01,970 --> 00:20:05,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Goodness me. You're such 
an amateur, Fu-kun.</font>

304
00:20:05,590 --> 00:20:09,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't forget that I'm an employee 
at a detective agency myself!</font>

305
00:20:09,810 --> 00:20:12,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're an amateur too. 
You're not a detective.</font>

306
00:20:13,900 --> 00:20:15,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They went into a building.</font>

307
00:20:24,400 --> 00:20:25,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you nervous?</font>

308
00:20:25,850 --> 00:20:28,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, very.</font>

309
00:20:35,960 --> 00:20:37,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fu-kun, where are you?!</font>

310
00:20:37,600 --> 00:20:39,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't leave me behind!</font>

311
00:20:39,590 --> 00:20:41,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is this glass? A window?!</font>

312
00:20:41,410 --> 00:20:43,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come on, Fu-kun!</font>

313
00:21:00,480 --> 00:21:02,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shizuka-san, right this way.</font>

314
00:21:04,740 --> 00:21:07,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A-Akira-san?</font>

315
00:21:15,570 --> 00:21:16,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I forgot.</font>

316
00:21:16,800 --> 00:21:21,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um... fancy meeting you here.</font>

317
00:21:21,160 --> 00:21:24,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry, but I'm working right now.</font>

318
00:21:24,470 --> 00:21:26,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can we talk later?</font>

319
00:21:27,730 --> 00:21:29,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Working?</font>

320
00:21:33,970 --> 00:21:37,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um, I'm sorry to interrupt, but...</font>

321
00:21:37,000 --> 00:21:38,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Big Brother?</font>

322
00:21:42,420 --> 00:21:44,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've been looking for you for so long...</font>

323
00:21:45,070 --> 00:21:47,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's been twenty years...</font>

324
00:21:47,570 --> 00:21:49,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I finally found you!</font>

325
00:21:57,630 --> 00:21:59,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How have you been?!</font>

326
00:21:59,940 --> 00:22:01,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm okay!</font>

327
00:22:01,680 --> 00:22:02,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really?!</font>

328
00:22:02,890 --> 00:22:04,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shall we give them some privacy?</font>

329
00:22:06,250 --> 00:22:08,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How about dinner?</font>

